  title: Where should I attach my logic scripts, in the parent or child object?
  text: Always aim to attach logic scripts to the parent object. The child/children
    should just handle visuals (like sprites), while the parent deals with logic
    and physics. Keeps things clean and avoids weird bugs down the line.
